  "body": "Output of `helm version`: v2.10.0\r\n\r\nI was surprised that when using the stable/postgresql chart, the PVC was not destroyed when i delete the Helm release.\r\n\r\nIn this chart, the default value for \"helm.sh/resource-policy\" annotation is \"\" and not \"keep\" so the PVC should be destroyed.\r\n\r\nAfter looking in pkg/tiller/resource_policy.go, seems that the \"if resourcePolicyType == keepPolicy\" should be complemented by an \"else\" that adds the manifest in the \"remaining\" array.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
